stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RESERVED

    RESERVED --> ENQUEUED: MQ 明确确认
    RESERVED --> SEND_UNKNOWN: 发送超时/结果未知
    RESERVED --> RELEASE_PENDING: 明确未发送且允许释放

    SEND_UNKNOWN --> ENQUEUED: 使用同一 message_id 补发成功
    SEND_UNKNOWN --> RELEASE_PENDING: 完成 MQ/DB 核查并建立围栏

    ENQUEUED --> ORDER_CREATED: PostgreSQL 订单事务成功
    ENQUEUED --> REJECTED: PostgreSQL 最终校验拒绝
    ENQUEUED --> RELEASE_PENDING: 对账确认不存在订单且消息已失效

    REJECTED --> RELEASE_PENDING
    RELEASE_PENDING --> RELEASED: 补偿 Lua 成功

    ORDER_CREATED --> [*]
    RELEASED --> [*]
